---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="DealFlow CRM — Project Details" description="Full-stack CRM with auth, Kanban pipeline, contacts and activities. Built with Next.js 15 + Supabase.">

  <a href="/mark-portfolio/#work" class="fixed top-6 left-6 z-40 inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full backdrop-blur-md bg-black/40 border border-white/10 text-sm text-ink-200 hover:text-accent-cyan hover:border-accent-cyan/40 transition">
    <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
    <span data-i18n="back">Back to portfolio</span>
  </a>

  <button id="lang-toggle" class="fixed top-6 right-6 z-40 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full backdrop-blur-md bg-black/40 border border-white/10 text-sm text-ink-200 hover:text-accent-cyan transition cursor-pointer">EN</button>

  <div class="min-h-screen py-20 px-4 md:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">

      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-14">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 mx-auto rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-400 to-blue-500 flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-2xl mb-6">D</div>
        <span class="section-label mx-auto" data-i18n="label">Project</span>
        <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-4xl md:text-5xl mt-4 mb-4" data-i18n="title">DealFlow CRM</h1>
        <p class="text-ink-400 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto" data-i18n="subtitle">
          A full-stack CRM application with real authentication, database, and deployment.
          Not a mockup. Not a simulation. A working app you can sign up for and use.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- CTA -->
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-3 justify-center mb-16">
        <a href="https://dealflow-crm-eta.vercel.app/demo" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-primary text-sm py-3 px-8 inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
          <span data-i18n="cta_demo">Try the live demo</span>
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 6H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 003 8.25v10.5A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0018 18.75V10.5m-10.5 6L21 3m0 0h-5.25M21 3v5.25"/></svg>
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/Mark1Anthony/dealflow-crm" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-ink-400 text-sm font-medium hover:text-accent-cyan transition py-3 px-8 border border-white/10 rounded-full hover:border-accent-cyan/30">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 0C5.37 0 0 5.37 0 12c0 5.31 3.435 9.795 8.205 11.385.6.105.825-.255.825-.57 0-.285-.015-1.23-.015-2.235-3.015.555-3.795-.735-4.035-1.41-.135-.345-.72-1.41-1.23-1.695-.42-.225-1.02-.78-.015-.795.945-.015 1.62.87 1.845 1.23 1.08 1.815 2.805 1.305 3.495.99.105-.78.42-1.305.765-1.605-2.67-.3-5.46-1.335-5.46-5.925 0-1.305.465-2.385 1.23-3.225-.12-.3-.54-1.53.12-3.18 0 0 1.005-.315 3.3 1.23.96-.27 1.98-.405 3-.405s2.04.135 3 .405c2.295-1.56 3.3-1.23 3.3-1.23.66 1.65.24 2.88.12 3.18.765.84 1.23 1.905 1.23 3.225 0 4.605-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.925.435.375.81 1.095.81 2.22 0 1.605-.015 2.895-.015 3.3 0 .315.225.69.825.57A12.02 12.02 0 0024 12c0-6.63-5.37-12-12-12z"/></svg>
          <span data-i18n="cta_code">View source code</span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Why I built this -->
      <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ink-50 mb-4" data-i18n="why_title">Why I built this</h2>
        <p class="text-ink-300 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4" data-i18n="why_text_1">
          Most portfolio projects are frontend demos that simulate data in the browser.
          They look impressive at first glance but fall apart when you check the code.
          No database, no auth, no real CRUD operations.
        </p>
        <p class="text-ink-300 text-sm leading-relaxed" data-i18n="why_text_2">
          DealFlow is different. It has a real PostgreSQL database with 7 tables.
          Real authentication where you sign up with an email and password.
          Row Level Security so one user can never see another user's data.
          Server Actions that validate input with Zod, write to the database, and revalidate the page.
          45 passing tests and CI that runs on every push.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- What it does -->
      <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ink-50 mb-4" data-i18n="what_title">What the app does</h2>
        <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-cyan-500/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-cyan-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15 19.128a9.38 9.38 0 002.625.372 9.337 9.337 0 004.121-.952 4.125 4.125 0 00-7.533-2.493M15 19.128v-.003c0-1.113-.285-2.16-.786-3.07M15 19.128v.106A12.318 12.318 0 018.624 21c-2.331 0-4.512-.645-6.374-1.766l-.001-.109a6.375 6.375 0 0111.964-3.07M12 6.375a3.375 3.375 0 11-6.75 0 3.375 3.375 0 016.75 0zm8.25 2.25a2.625 2.625 0 11-5.25 0 2.625 2.625 0 015.25 0z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div><div class="text-ink-100 text-sm font-semibold" data-i18n="feat_contacts_title">Contacts</div><div class="text-ink-400 text-xs" data-i18n="feat_contacts_desc">Create, edit, search, delete. With company, email, phone, notes.</div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-violet-500/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-violet-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9 4.5v15m6-15v15m-10.875 0h15.75c.621 0 1.125-.504 1.125-1.125V5.625c0-.621-.504-1.125-1.125-1.125H4.125C3.504 4.5 3 5.004 3 5.625v12.75c0 .621.504 1.125 1.125 1.125z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div><div class="text-ink-100 text-sm font-semibold" data-i18n="feat_kanban_title">Kanban Pipeline</div><div class="text-ink-400 text-xs" data-i18n="feat_kanban_desc">Drag deals between stages. Lead, Qualified, Proposal, Won, Lost.</div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-amber-500/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-amber-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 13.125C3 12.504 3.504 12 4.125 12h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v6.75C7.5 20.496 6.996 21 6.375 21h-2.25A1.125 1.125 0 013 19.875v-6.75zM9.75 8.625c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125v11.25c0 .621-.504 1.125-1.125 1.125h-2.25a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V8.625z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div><div class="text-ink-100 text-sm font-semibold" data-i18n="feat_dashboard_title">Dashboard</div><div class="text-ink-400 text-xs" data-i18n="feat_dashboard_desc">KPIs, pipeline overview, recent activity feed.</div></div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-3">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-emerald-500/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-emerald-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 6v6h4.5m4.5 0a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div><div class="text-ink-100 text-sm font-semibold" data-i18n="feat_activities_title">Activities</div><div class="text-ink-400 text-xs" data-i18n="feat_activities_desc">Log calls, emails, meetings, tasks. Filter by type.</div></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Tech decisions -->
      <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ink-50 mb-4" data-i18n="tech_title">Tech decisions</h2>
        <div class="space-y-4 text-sm">
          <div class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-accent-cyan font-mono font-bold w-40 flex-shrink-0">Next.js 15</span><span class="text-ink-300" data-i18n="tech_next">Server Components + Server Actions. No separate API layer needed for CRUD. Forms submit directly to server functions.</span></div>
          <div class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-accent-cyan font-mono font-bold w-40 flex-shrink-0">Supabase Auth</span><span class="text-ink-300" data-i18n="tech_auth">Email/password auth with cookie-based sessions. Middleware guards every route. No token management in the frontend.</span></div>
          <div class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-accent-cyan font-mono font-bold w-40 flex-shrink-0">PostgreSQL + RLS</span><span class="text-ink-300" data-i18n="tech_rls">7 tables with Row Level Security. Every query is automatically scoped to the authenticated user. No data leaks possible at the DB level.</span></div>
          <div class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-accent-cyan font-mono font-bold w-40 flex-shrink-0">Zod</span><span class="text-ink-300" data-i18n="tech_zod">Runtime validation on every form submission. Types inferred from schemas, so the frontend and backend always agree on the shape of data.</span></div>
          <div class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-accent-cyan font-mono font-bold w-40 flex-shrink-0">@hello-pangea/dnd</span><span class="text-ink-300" data-i18n="tech_dnd">Kanban drag-and-drop with optimistic updates. If the server call fails, the UI rolls back to the previous state.</span></div>
          <div class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-accent-cyan font-mono font-bold w-40 flex-shrink-0">Vitest</span><span class="text-ink-300" data-i18n="tech_vitest">45 passing tests covering validation schemas and utility functions. CI runs typecheck + tests + build on every push.</span></div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Architecture -->
      <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ink-50 mb-4" data-i18n="arch_title">Architecture</h2>
        <pre class="text-ink-400 text-xs font-mono leading-relaxed overflow-x-auto">src/
├── app/
│   ├── (auth)/login/          Login/Signup
│   ├── (app)/                 Authenticated routes
│   │   ├── dashboard/         KPIs + pipeline + activity feed
│   │   ├── contacts/          List, detail, create, edit
│   │   ├── deals/             Kanban board, detail, create, edit
│   │   ├── activities/        Filterable activity feed
│   │   └── settings/          Pipeline stage editor
│   └── api/                   PATCH endpoint for Kanban drag
├── components/                UI components (Sidebar, Kanban, Forms)
├── lib/
│   ├── queries/               Server-side data fetching
│   ├── actions/               Server Actions for mutations
│   ├── types.ts               TypeScript interfaces
│   └── validation.ts          Zod schemas
└── middleware.ts              Auth guard</pre>
      </div>

      <!-- Database -->
      <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 mb-8">
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ink-50 mb-4" data-i18n="db_title">Database</h2>
        <p class="text-ink-400 text-sm mb-4" data-i18n="db_desc">7 tables with foreign keys, CHECK constraints, indexes, and RLS policies on every table.</p>
        <pre class="text-ink-400 text-xs font-mono leading-relaxed">pipeline_stages  ←──  deals  ──→  contacts
                        │              │
                      notes          notes
                        │              │
                    activities     activities
                                      │
                                 contact_tags  ──→  tags</pre>
      </div>

      <!-- How to try it -->
      <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12">
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-xl text-ink-50 mb-4" data-i18n="howto_title">How to try it</h2>
        <ol class="text-ink-300 text-sm leading-relaxed space-y-2 list-decimal list-inside">
          <li data-i18n="howto_1">Click "Try the live demo" above</li>
          <li data-i18n="howto_2">No signup needed, a demo account is created automatically</li>
          <li data-i18n="howto_3">Demo data is loaded for you</li>
          <li data-i18n="howto_4">Drag deals between stages, create contacts, log activities</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <!-- Bottom CTA -->
      <div class="text-center">
        <a href="https://dealflow-crm-eta.vercel.app/demo" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-primary text-base py-4 px-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
          <span data-i18n="cta_demo_bottom">Try the live demo</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M13.5 6H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 003 8.25v10.5A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h10.5A2.25 2.25 0 0018 18.75V10.5m-10.5 6L21 3m0 0h-5.25M21 3v5.25"/></svg>
        </a>
        <p class="text-ink-500 text-xs mt-4" data-i18n="cta_note">No sign-up needed. Demo account is created automatically.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

<script>
const t = {
